Invocation Name: trinity lincoln
des: Listen to the latest sermon from Trinity United Methodist Church in Lincoln, Nebraska! You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. You can also ask for previous and next sermons by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next" or "Alexa, shuffle" for a random one.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
